Brandon, some tips for the next 2 plagues:

The Nano Virus:

You need to be fast. It‚Äôs a race against the clock
Evolve insomnia and paranoia immediately. It will cost you 1 dna point in total 
Transmission is key and don‚Äôt worry about evolving lethal symptoms too early. You need to kill the planet off as fast as possible

The Nano Virus is a man made virus that escaped. The Cure will start instantly and it will go fast
Evolve the special abilities to slow down the cure

The Bio Weapon:
Same as a normal plague but with a qwerk:

Every week, theatre is a chance that you will gain lethality. You did nothing to make it grow.
There are special abilities to help delay or reduce the lethality. After you get all the special abilities, an special one appears
That evolution makes the plague go into Armageddon. It will fill you lethality to 100 percent.

I hope this helps you in your endeavours
